$ hdwwiz.cpl

*Add Hardware → Windows/control-panel[Control Panel] Applet*

sa:
  Apparently, there is a relationship to the → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/devmgmt_msc[Device Manager (`devmgmt.msc`)]: When using
  → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/control_exe[`control.exe`] with `hdwwiz.cpl` it opens the same window as when typing `devmgmt.msc` into
  → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/cmd_exe[`cmd.exe`]:

code {
C:\> → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/control_exe[control] hdwwiz.cpl
C:\> → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/devmgmt_msc[devmgmt.msc]
code }
